data.description: Resort Style living in Sun City Anthem!  Located in the highly sought after 55+ Community of Sun City Anthem, this popular Andover model offers a serene backyard paradise complete with hot tub, built-in BBQ, fully fenced backyard and beautiful outdoor solar screens for your year round enjoyment.  Light and bright upgraded home boasts PAID OFF SOLAR panels, Smart Stainless Steel appliances, new kitchen counter tops and sink, new flooring in front rooms, NUVO cartridge water softener plus so much more.  As part of the Sun City Anthem community you will have access to a gorgeous clubhouse with Strip Views, indoor and outdoor resort style pools, state of the art fitness center, exercise classes and indoor walking track.  COMMUNITY GOLF, PICKLEBALL, TENNIS, Billiards, Bocci, Poker, Ceramics, Sewing Professional Woodworking Shop, Theatre and more.  2804 Goldcreek is a place to call home!
